    {
      "parameters": {
        "color": 1,
        "width": 520,
        "height": 340,
        "content": "### How it works\nThis inactive template collects a capped public sample from Meta Ads Library, Google Ads Transparency, and TikTok Creative Center Actors, normalizes only comparable evidence, compares with the previous snapshot, optionally classifies hooks and offers in one structured AI request, then writes one Markdown brief to Google Drive. It preserves source statuses and source-specific signals without creating a cross-network score.\n\n### Setup\nUse the setup form or config Data Table for watchlist label, market, source queries, weekly window, item cap, Drive folder, and optional Slack notification. Add Apify and Google Drive credentials in n8n. OpenAI and Slack are optional. Keep the workflow inactive until QA/publisher approval."
      },
